{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase the minimum sentence for illegal possession of a knife to 20 years",
        "additional_details": "Too many people are needlessly being stabbed. There is almost never a good reason to carry a knife in public but many feel they can carry, and use, knives without the fear of appropriate punishment.\r\n \r\nMake the punishment so strong that people will stop carrying and using knives.\r\n",
        "background": "We want anyone found carrying a knife, without very good reason, to be automatically given a 20-year prison sentence as a minimum.",
